{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:12:59.986009+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here are the **setup and day-to-day development commands** for this repository, sourced from `package.json` and `README.md`:\n\n---\n\n### Prerequisites\n- **Package manager:** `pnpm` (v10.20.0, enforced via `preinstall` script)\n- **Node version:** see `.nvmrc`\n\n---\n\n### Install dependencies\n```bash\npnpm install\n```\n\n### Dev server (hot-reload)\n```bash\npnpm run dev\n```\n\n### Production build\n```bash\npnpm run build\n```\n\n### Preview a production build locally\n```bash\npnpm run preview        # serve the dist/ folder\npnpm run build-preview  # build then preview in one step\n```\n\n### Unit tests (Vitest)\n```bash\npnpm run test:unit            # run in watch mode\npnpm run test:unit-coverage   # single run with coverage\n```\n\n### Lint (ESLint)\n```bash\npnpm run lint        # check all .vue, .ts, .js files\npnpm run lint-fix    # auto-fix lint issues\n```\n\n---\n\n### Additional tooling in place\n| Tool | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| **Husky** (`pnpm run prepare`) | Git hooks setup (runs automatically after install) |\n| **Commitlint** | Enforces conventional commit messages |\n| **lint-staged** | Runs linters on staged files at commit time |\n| **Prettier** | Code formatting |\n| **Semantic Release** | Automated versioning and release |\n\n---\n\n### Verification files\n\n**`package.json` (scripts section):**\n```json\n{\n  \"preinstall\": \"npx only-allow pnpm\",\n  \"dev\": \"vite\",\n  \"build\": \"vite build\",\n  \"preview\": \"vite preview\",\n  \"build-preview\": \"vite build && vite preview\",\n  \"lint\": \"eslint \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n  \"lint-fix\": \"eslint --fix \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n  \"test:unit\": \"vitest\",\n  \"test:unit-coverage\": \"vitest run --coverage\",\n  \"prepare\": \"husky\"\n}\n```\n\n**`src/router/index.js`:**\n```js\nimport { createRouter, createWebHashHistory } from 'vue-router'\nimport Home from '../views/Home.vue'\n\nconst history = createWebHashHistory()\nconst routes = [\n  {\n    path: '/',\n    name: 'Home',\n    component: Home,\n    meta: { layout: 'default' },\n  },\n  {\n    path: '/about',\n    name: 'About',\n    component: () => import(/* webpackChunkName: \"about\" */ '../views/About.vue'),\n    meta: { layout: 'default' },\n  },\n]\nconst router = createRouter({\n  linkActiveClass: 'active',\n  history,\n  routes,\n})\n\nexport { router }\n```", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 660, "prompt_tokens": 9627, "total_tokens": 10287, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 34, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 9280, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.000758553, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.000184353, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.0005742}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780863169-Kyb2PyqQAgquEQcBYrul", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3b7-72da-7cd3-b79b-8fdc8bec4a1e-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9627, "output_tokens": 660, "total_tokens": 10287, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 9280}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 34}}}}]}}}
